Package: ftp-simulator
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: FTP Simulator Team <admin@example.com>
Depends: adduser, docker-ce | docker.io | docker-ce-rootless-extras
Recommends: docker-compose-plugin
Section: finance
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://example.com/ftp-simulator
Description: FTP Simulator — Funds Transfer Pricing engine
 A complete FTP calculation engine supporting MMFTP, Duration, Pool,
 Flux, Refinancing, Floating-Rate, Behavioral, Replicating Portfolio,
 and LDI methods. Includes a web dashboard and PostgreSQL backend.
 .
 On first run the installer downloads PostgreSQL 18 from your configured
 FTP server and sets up the database automatically.
